data.description: Beautiful brick ranch on corner lot. This spacious home features 3 bedrooms and 2 tile baths, fabulous kitchen with plenty of cabinets and counter space. A welcoming broken-tile front porch opens to foyer and beautiful living room. Gorgeous vaulted ceiling with beams and fireplace in den. Textured walls, wood and tile floors, new carpet, new interior paint. Beautiful bedrooms with walk-in closets. Large utility room opens to double carport with storage. Large rear deck and pergola are perfect outdoor entertainment areas. Detached storage building lighted and floored. Fenced back yard.
